review_blob:
33cl Bottle bought @Vinmonopolet Haugesund. 
Pops like a champagne when i opened it. 
Color of dark cola with a few sparkling bubbles.
Aroma of Caramel and liccorice. Oily palate Light bitter and sweet.

Bought a can at Vinmonopolet. love the artwork, looks pretty.
Taste is good for a pilsner. Its better than most pilsners i have tasted before.
color is golden. Taste is somehow crispy with a nice Berry-ish flavour.

Bottle. Dark brown almost black color with thick beige head. aroma of coffee, mocca, caramel and bark. Taste has a small hint of caramel and leather. Feels too watery on the taste. feels like something is missing
Bottle bougth in gourmet junk burger. Golden color with Thin white head and small carbonation. Taste fresh, kinda like citrus. Really good alcohol free choice.
Bottle bougth at Gnu in Stavanger. Light golden color with white head. Aroma of wheat and citrus. Taste really sour wheath beer. Love sour drinks. Cheers!

Bottle 0,33L. GOlden orange color with thin white bubbly head. aroma of oranges, spruce and earthy leaves. Honestly, I loved this beer before. All my friends think its great, but Ive somehow lost it (Probably that time I got very sick straight after I drank one.). I feel like the taste is missing something. It just taste Bitter. Bitter all the way. I like bitter beers, but I miss something on this one.

Bottle. Golden Orange color with thin white bubbly head. Aroma of wheat, White chocolate and floral. Taste is boring. I think this one gets a lower score than it deserves, but this is the boringest and most dissapointing wheat beer i have ever tasted (So far).
Bottle @ a friend. Night-black color with creamy beige head. Aroma of smoke and Chocolate cake. Taste of Coffee, Chocolate and roasted malts.

Bottle bought @ Vinmonopolet in Ski. Hazed golden color with thin white head. Aroma of citrus, Orange and hop. Light sweet and a small bitter finish. 
A little creamy feeling drinking this. Not what I hoped for unfortunately...
Bottle. Dark brown Almost blank black an a little red color and beige head. Aroma of creamed coffee and caramel. Taste of cream, toffee, coffee and whiskey. Jesus this was a good beer. Reccomended
Bougth in Oslo. Bottle. Orange-dark color with small white head. Small carbonation. Smells really good, aroma of orange and hops. Taste of light fanta-ish. A good swedish beer

Bottle bougth in vinmonopolet. Fresh golden colour, Thin white bubbely head and small carbonation. Taste just as fresh as it looks. With aroma of wit, floral, citrus and mango. Good taste of summer. Nice
Bottle. Boring standard pilsner format. Taste works in the heating sun, but not elsewhere. Boring... Felt like I have been drinking this many times before..

Bought a pint in shetlands "The Loungue" while on a school trip. Bronze-dark color with thin white head. Aroma of red berries,leather and hoppy grass. Taste of alcohol, citrus and bark. Not my kind of beer.
Can bought in Cuba several times. Golden lager color with little carbon. Smells like metal, alcohol and a little hops. Taste light sweet. My favourite beer in my class-trip to cuba.
Bottle bougth at meny. Golden carbonating clean golden. Taste medium bitter, light sweet .
Bottle bougth at samson. Looks like a regular pilsner. Clear golden color with white head. Smell of alcohol, floral, metal and breakfast. Not a good taste. Works for the hot summer sun
Bottle bought at Kiwi daily store. light golden with white head. light carbon. smell of floral, bark, hay and citrus. Citrusfloral taste with light aftertaste. A little boring in my opinion.
Bottle bougth at Apollon platebar. Black with small beige head. Smell of coffee and red berries. Taste of coffee, medium bitter.
Tap, bougth at Apollon platebar. Golden color with small white head. Smell of weath and alcohol. Taste of wheath. Mild and light bitter.
330ml bottle bougth at Apollon platebar. Black with thick beige head. Smell of hops, grass and leather. Taste really bitter. A little bit too bitter.

Looks: Light Brown with thick Beige Spiderweb-ish head
Smell: Smell of fall, Citrus, grass, ginger and bark.
Taste: Light Bitter, medium sweet.
Bought it at Vinmonopolet. Soundet really intresting. Really good.

Been drinking alot of tuborg. its Cheap, not to hard to drink and is mostly quite refreshing after a hard day at work or in the heating sun... Im still not a fan of it. I would rather have much other beers over tuborg. Clear Golden with white head. Smell of Metal, floral and alcohol. Medium sweet and a light bitter finish.
Bottle got as a christmas gift from a friend. Red-ish dark color with beige head. Smells like akevitt, floral and Sugar. Medium sweet.

Bottle. Dark Black colour and Thin beige head. Smell of cherries, coffee and floral. Taste of Soda, coffee and redberries. 
Good taste. Porter love
UPDATED: DEC 19, 2014
Bottle @ Apollon platebar. Smell of ginger and coffee. Dark blac colour. Beige head. Taste sweet, light bitter.

Bottle bougth at kvarteret in Bergen. Dark black color and small cute beige head. Smell like chocolate and coffee. Taste like chocolate and roasted coffee beans. Not a fan of imperial stouts but i like this.
Bottle bougth at Apollon platebar. Smells like good roasted christmas meat. Taste like roasted coffee beans, ribbs. Carbonated feeling.
Bottle shared with a friend @ Apollon platebar. Smells like gummybears, Apple and a sweet summer beer. Taste surprisingly sweet for a christmas beer. Not sure if worth the pride through
Bottle. Orange light color and thick white head. Smell off fall. Wheat and hops. Tasted delicious. One of the best wheatbeers i have tasted.
Bougth at @ Apollon in Bergen. Beautifull appearance. Black with beige head. Smells like pork, meat and coffee. This is the best christmas beer i have tasted. So far
Bottle bougth @ Apollon. Orange see through color. Smells like champagne, sour Apple and grapes. Taste is sour, medium sweet. Like champagne.

Bottle. colour is cloudy lager. thick white head. smells like citrus, earthy.
heavy cloying sweetness, lightly bitter.
Bottle. clear golden color. taste of berries and grass.smell of grass and sour berries. too mild like a pale lager

Bottle 0,25L. Shared with a friend. Color reminds me of cheap cola, mix between dark and light brown. smell of sour cherries, smoky, yeasty. 
medium bitterness, light sweetness.
Bougth at Apollon platebar. Totaly black with small beige head. Smell of hot chocolate and caramel. Taste of chocolate, Sugar and leaves. Sweet and bitter taste.
Bottle bougth at Apollon platebar. Looks realy Amazing. seethrough brownies with white head. Smell of red wine, grass, caramel and leaves. Taste of caramel. Sweet.
Bottle. Bougth at Apollon platebar. Golden brown color. White head. Smell of licorice, grass and leather. Taste of hop Sugar and leaves. Surprisingly good.
Bottle. Dark golden. still light. I got no head a all weird enough. Smell of citrus, sugar, honey. taste of Mild sweet. Fruity somehow. A little bit spice and citrus.
Bottle. berry-red-brown color. Aroma of malt and rasberry. Taste of Strawberries, rasberries, grass and citrus. creamy, astringent. Really good. Would like this for a creamy dessert.

Bottle from Vinmonopolet. Light and dark brown color. tan head. Clear but too dark to see through. Aroma og leather, smoke, dried fruits and meat. Taste of Meat, light smoke and red fruits. medium sweetness. Easy to drink. Not too smoky in my opinion, but a surprisingly eady taste. but could be much more smoked.
Bottle. Dark golden color, see through. White thick head. Smell of hop, rootbeer and a little soda water. Taste of hop, berries, leather and floral.
Bottle. Golden color. Small carbonation. Taste of alcohol, grass and red berries. I dont have much og a smell today. But as far as i can tell there is a little berry in it.
Bottle. Brown orange with white bubbly head. Smells extrdmey good. Blackberry-ish sour smell. Litterally taste like a basement (like it smells). Like it. It was average.
Can. Black with beige head. Really good smell of coconut, coffee and raisins. Taste of raisins. Carbonated. Palate is watery. Good one
Bottle. Brown light yellow colour. Almost like piss. Smells like aprico, fruits. Taste bitter, fruity. Summerfeeling. Good
beer_name: To l Dangerously Close to Stupid

review_blob: Bottle. Looks like a pilsner. Smell not so good. Sour. Taste of sweet pear, Sugar, sour Apples. Good taste for a cider
Bottle @ stuelands. Black with beige head. Smell of chocolate and coffee. Taste of coffee beans, chocolate, caramel and Sugar. Good palate. Great for dessert.
Bottle. Light brown yellow and think white head. Smell of apricot, citrus and leather. Taste of citrus, hops and apricot. Light bitter and light sweet.
